<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{.title}} - h3sync</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/admin.css">
  <script src="/static/admin.js"></script>
  <style>
    .gen-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr; gap: 24px; align-items: start; }
    .gen-panel { background: #fff; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: var(--shadow); border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
    .result-tabs { display: flex; gap: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color); margin-bottom: 16px; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 4px; }
    .result-tab-btn { background: transparent; border: none; padding: 8px 16px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted); border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; margin-bottom: -6px; }
    .result-tab-btn.active { color: var(--primary); border-bottom-color: var(--primary); }
    .result-content { display: none; }
    .result-content.active { display: block; }
    .code-box { position: relative; background: #111827; color: #e5e7eb; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-family: Consolas, "SFMono-Regular", monospace; overflow-x: auto; font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.5; white-space: pre-wrap; min-height: 320px; }
    .btn-copy-code { position: absolute; top: 8px; right: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); color: #fff; border: none; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .btn-copy-code:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
    .hint-card { margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 16px; border-radius: 12px; background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); }
    .hint-card h4 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .hint-card p { margin: 0; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }
    .rule-list { display: grid; gap: 10px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .rule-item { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center; padding: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border-color); border-radius: 10px; background: #fff; }
    .rule-item input[type="checkbox"] { width: auto; flex: 0 0 auto; margin: 0; align-self: center; }
    .rule-item-content { min-width: 0; flex: 1; }
    .rule-item strong { display: block; margin: 0; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
    .rule-item p { display: none; }
    .rule-item-content[title] { cursor: help; }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) { .gen-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="app-container">
    {{template "sidebar" .}}

    <div class="mobile-header">
      <div class="mobile-site-brand" style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem;">h3sync</div>
      <button class="menu-toggle"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg></button>
    </div>

    <main class="main-content">
      <div class="card-title" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <h2>Agent 生成与配置中心</h2>
      </div>

      {{if .message}}
      <div class="card" style="background:#f0f9ff; border-color:#bae6fd; color:#0369a1; padding:12px 24px; margin-bottom:24px;">{{.message}}</div>
      {{end}}

      <div class="gen-grid">
        <div class="gen-panel">
          <div class="hint-card">
            <h4>企业信息联动</h4>
            <p>
              这里仅联动企业信息，不带入平台网站名称、Logo、域名等网站配置。
              {{if not .basicConfig.CompanyName}}如需完整企业背景，请先到 <a href="/admin/basic-settings">基本设置</a> 补充企业资料。{{end}}
            </p>
          </div>

          <h3 style="margin-bottom:20px; font-size:1.1rem;">基础信息</h3>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Agent 名称</label>
            <input id="agentName" type="text" placeholder="例如：EnterpriseSupportAgent" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>Host / 根接口地址</label>
            <input id="projectUrl" type="text" value="{{if .host}}http://{{.host}}{{else}}http://localhost:8080{{end}}" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>工作目录</label>
            <input id="workDir" type="text" value="/workspace" />
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>API Key</label>
            <select id="apiKey">
              <option value="">-- 请选择一个已创建的 API Key --</option>
              {{range .keys}}
              <option value="{{.KeyValue}}">{{.Name}}{{if .Remark}} ({{.Remark}}){{end}}</option>
              {{end}}
            </select>
            <small style="color:var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.75rem;">Agent 在调用 OpenAPI 接口时会直接使用这里选定的密钥。</small>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group" style="margin-top:24px;">
            <label style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
              <span>角色定义</span>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm" onclick="openModal('roleModal')">管理角色库</button>
            </label>
            <select id="roleSelector" onchange="loadRoleContent(this)">
              <option value="">-- 选择一个已保存的角色预设 --</option>
              {{range .roles}}
              <option value="{{.ID}}" data-content="{{.Content}}">{{.Name}}</option>
              {{end}}
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>自定义角色说明</label>
            <textarea id="roleContent" rows="8" placeholder="输入 Agent 的定位、行为风格、职责边界和工作原则。"></textarea>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group" style="margin-top:24px;">
            <label style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;">
              <span>核心规则</span>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm" onclick="openModal('coreRuleModal')">管理核心规则</button>
            </label>
            <div class="rule-list">
              {{range .coreRules}}
              <label class="rule-item">
                <input type="checkbox" class="core-rule-checkbox" value="{{.ID}}" data-name="{{.Name}}" data-content="{{.Content}}" />
                <div class="rule-item-content" title="{{.Content}}">
                  <strong>{{.Name}}</strong>
                </div>
              </label>
              {{else}}
              <div class="rule-item">
                <div class="rule-item-content">
                  <strong>暂无核心规则</strong>
                </div>
              </div>
              {{end}}
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label>补充核心规则</label>
            <textarea id="customCoreRules" rows="4" placeholder="可补充当前 Agent 特有的长期固定规则。"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 100%; margin-top:16px;" onclick="generateAgentDocs()">生成 MD 预览</button>
        </div>

        <div class="gen-panel">
          <div class="result-tabs">
            <button class="result-tab-btn active" onclick="switchResTab('AGENTS_MD', this)">AGENTS.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('SOUL_MD', this)">SOUL.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('TOOLS_MD', this)">TOOLS.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('IDENTITY_MD', this)">IDENTITY.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('HEARTBEAT_MD', this)">HEARTBEAT.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('BOOTSTRAP_MD', this)">BOOTSTRAP.md</button>
            <button class="result-tab-btn" onclick="switchResTab('MEMORY_MD', this)">MEMORY.md</button>
          </div>

          <div id="AGENTS_MD" class="result-content active">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('AGENTS_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="AGENTS_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="SOUL_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('SOUL_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="SOUL_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="TOOLS_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('TOOLS_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="TOOLS_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="IDENTITY_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('IDENTITY_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="IDENTITY_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="HEARTBEAT_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('HEARTBEAT_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="HEARTBEAT_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="BOOTSTRAP_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('BOOTSTRAP_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="BOOTSTRAP_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
          <div id="MEMORY_MD" class="result-content">
            <div class="code-box"><button class="btn-copy-code" onclick="copyContent('MEMORY_MD_RAW')">复制</button><div id="MEMORY_MD_RAW">配置尚未生成...</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </div>

  <div id="roleModal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal-content" style="max-width: 600px;">
      <div class="card-title">
        <span>角色库管理</span>
        <button type="button" onclick="closeModal('roleModal')" class="btn-close-large">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; max-height: 200px; overflow-y: auto;">
        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd; text-align:left;">角色名称</th>
              <th style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd; text-align:right;">操作</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {{range .roles}}
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;">{{.Name}}</td>
              <td style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:right;">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm" style="padding:4px 8px; margin-right:4px;" onclick="editRoleTemplate(this)" data-name="{{.Name}}" data-content="{{.Content}}">编辑</button>
                <form method="post" action="/admin/agent-gen/roles/{{.ID}}/delete" onsubmit="return confirm('确定删除该角色预设？');" style="display:inline;">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm danger" style="padding:4px 8px;">删除</button>
                </form>
              </td>
            </tr>
            {{else}}
            <tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; padding:16px; color:#999;">暂无角色预设</td></tr>
            {{end}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <h4 style="margin-bottom:12px;">新增 / 编辑角色预设</h4>
      <form method="post" action="/admin/agent-gen/roles">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="角色名称，例如：企业资料问答助手" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <textarea name="content" rows="6" placeholder="输入角色目标、适用场景和行为风格。" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:right;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">保存角色</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="coreRuleModal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal-content" style="max-width: 600px;">
      <div class="card-title">
        <span>核心规则库</span>
        <button type="button" onclick="closeModal('coreRuleModal')" class="btn-close-large">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 24px; max-height: 200px; overflow-y: auto;">
        <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse;">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd; text-align:left;">规则名称</th>
              <th style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #ddd; text-align:right;">操作</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {{range .coreRules}}
            <tr>
              <td style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;">{{.Name}}</td>
              <td style="padding:8px; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:right;">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm" style="padding:4px 8px; margin-right:4px;" onclick="editCoreRuleTemplate(this)" data-name="{{.Name}}" data-content="{{.Content}}">编辑</button>
                <form method="post" action="/admin/agent-gen/core-rules/{{.ID}}/delete" onsubmit="return confirm('确定删除该核心规则？');" style="display:inline;">
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm danger" style="padding:4px 8px;">删除</button>
                </form>
              </td>
            </tr>
            {{else}}
            <tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; padding:16px; color:#999;">暂无核心规则</td></tr>
            {{end}}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <h4 style="margin-bottom:12px;">新增 / 编辑核心规则</h4>
      <form method="post" action="/admin/agent-gen/core-rules">
        <div class="form-group">
          <input id="coreRuleNameInput" type="text" name="name" placeholder="规则名称，例如：禁止删除业务数据" required />
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <textarea id="coreRuleContentInput" name="content" rows="6" placeholder="输入长期固定的核心约束规则。" required></textarea>
        </div>
        <div style="text-align:right;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">保存核心规则</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="toast" style="position:fixed; bottom:30px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); background:#1e293b; color:#fff; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:99px; font-size:0.875rem; opacity:0; transition:all 0.3s; pointer-events:none; z-index:1000; box-shadow:0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);"></div>

  <div
    id="basic-config-source"
    data-company-name="{{.basicConfig.CompanyName}}"
    data-company-address="{{.basicConfig.CompanyAddress}}"
    data-company-phone="{{.basicConfig.CompanyPhone}}"
    data-company-email="{{.basicConfig.CompanyEmail}}"
    data-company-website="{{.basicConfig.CompanyWebsite}}"
    data-working-hours="{{.basicConfig.WorkingHours}}"
    data-company-intro="{{.basicConfig.CompanyIntro}}"
    hidden
  ></div>
  <script>
    const basicConfigSource = document.getElementById('basic-config-source');
    const basicConfig = {
      company_name: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyName || '' : '',
      company_address: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyAddress || '' : '',
      company_phone: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyPhone || '' : '',
      company_email: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyEmail || '' : '',
      company_website: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyWebsite || '' : '',
      working_hours: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.workingHours || '' : '',
      company_intro: basicConfigSource ? basicConfigSource.dataset.companyIntro || '' : ''
    };

    function loadRoleContent(sel) {
      if (sel.options[sel.selectedIndex]) {
        const txt = sel.options[sel.selectedIndex].getAttribute('data-content');
        if (txt) document.getElementById('roleContent').value = txt;
      }
    }

    function editRoleTemplate(btn) {
      const formName = document.querySelector('#roleModal input[name="name"]');
      const formContent = document.querySelector('#roleModal textarea[name="content"]');
      formName.value = btn.getAttribute('data-name');
      formContent.value = btn.getAttribute('data-content');
      formName.focus();
    }

    function editCoreRuleTemplate(btn) {
      document.getElementById('coreRuleNameInput').value = btn.getAttribute('data-name');
      document.getElementById('coreRuleContentInput').value = btn.getAttribute('data-content');
      document.getElementById('coreRuleNameInput').focus();
    }

    function switchResTab(id, btn) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.result-tab-btn').forEach((tabBtn) => tabBtn.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.result-content').forEach((content) => content.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById(id).classList.add('active');
    }

    function copyContent(domId) {
      const txt = document.getElementById(domId).textContent || document.getElementById(domId).innerText;
      if (navigator.clipboard && navigator.clipboard.writeText) {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(txt).then(() => showToast('内容已复制到剪贴板'));
        return;
      }
      const ta = document.createElement('textarea');
      ta.value = txt;
      document.body.appendChild(ta);
      ta.select();
      document.execCommand('copy');
      document.body.removeChild(ta);
      showToast('内容已复制到剪贴板');
    }

    function showToast(msg) {
      const toast = document.getElementById('toast');
      toast.innerText = msg;
      toast.style.opacity = '1';
      setTimeout(() => { toast.style.opacity = '0'; }, 3000);
    }

    function line(label, value) {
      return `${label}: ${value || '未设置'}`;
    }

    function selectedCoreRules() {
      const selected = [];
      document.querySelectorAll('.core-rule-checkbox:checked').forEach((item) => {
        selected.push(`- ${item.getAttribute('data-name')}: ${item.getAttribute('data-content')}`);
      });
      const custom = document.getElementById('customCoreRules').value.trim();
      if (custom) {
        selected.push(`- 补充规则: ${custom}`);
      }
      return selected.length ? selected.join('\n') : '- 未配置核心规则';
    }

    function enterpriseBlock() {
      return [
        '## 企业基础资料',
        line('企业名称', basicConfig.company_name),
        line('企业地址', basicConfig.company_address),
        line('联系方式', basicConfig.company_phone),
        line('联系邮箱', basicConfig.company_email),
        line('企业官网', basicConfig.company_website),
        line('工作时间', basicConfig.working_hours),
        line('企业说明', basicConfig.company_intro),
        ''
      ].join('\n');
    }

    function apiUsageBlock(url, key) {
      return [
        '## API 调用规范',
        '1. 所有请求都必须携带请求头 `X-API-Key`，不得省略、不得替换为其他自定义头。',
        '2. 开始工作前必须先调用表单发现接口，不允许凭空猜测 schema code 或字段名。',
        `3. 表单发现接口：\`GET ${url}/openapi/forms\``,
        '4. 拿到 schema code 后，先读取字段结构，再决定查询条件。',
        `5. 字段结构接口：\`GET ${url}/openapi/forms/{schema}\``,
        '6. 查询数据时优先使用精确过滤，避免一次性拉取过多无关数据。',
        `7. 数据查询接口：\`POST ${url}/openapi/query/{schema}\``,
        '8. 若接口返回无权限、无数据、字段不存在或 schema 不存在，必须原样说明，不得自行猜测补全。',
        '9. 企业资料库、H3 表单、MSSQL 表单都属于同一套 OpenAPI 访问面，应按授权结果决定可用范围。',
        '10. 返回结果时应明确指出使用的表单、关键字段和值来源。',
        '',
        '### 标准请求头',
        '```http',
        `X-API-Key: ${key}`,
        'Content-Type: application/json',
        '```',
        '',
        '### 表单发现示例',
        '```bash',
        `curl -X GET "${url}/openapi/forms" \\`,
        `  -H "X-API-Key: ${key}"`,
        '```',
        '',
        '### 字段结构示例',
        '```bash',
        `curl -X GET "${url}/openapi/forms/{schema}" \\`,
        `  -H "X-API-Key: ${key}"`,
        '```',
        '',
        '### 数据查询示例',
        '```bash',
        `curl -X POST "${url}/openapi/query/{schema}" \\`,
        `  -H "X-API-Key: ${key}" \\`,
        '  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\',
        '  -d \'{',
        '    "filters": [',
        '      { "field": "keyword", "op": "contains", "value": "示例关键词" }',
        '    ],',
        '    "page": 1,',
        '    "size": 20',
        '  }\'',
        '```'
      ].join('\n');
    }

    function constraintBlock() {
      return [
        '## Agent 约束',
        '1. 只允许基于系统内真实接口和真实数据回答，不允许虚构企业信息、联系人、地址、产品、价格、资质或政策。',
        '2. 未先完成 `/openapi/forms` 探测前，不允许直接构造 schema 查询。',
        '3. 遇到多张候选表时，必须先比较表单备注、字段定义和业务语义，再决定读取顺序。',
        '4. 若用户请求超出授权范围、超出表单数据范围或需要外部知识，必须明确说明边界。',
        '5. 不允许将网站展示配置误当成企业业务知识写入回答。',
        '6. 涉及联系方式、邮箱、官网、地址、工作时间时，优先引用基本设置中的企业信息。',
        '7. 未确认字段含义前，不允许将自由文本字段解释为确定事实。',
        '8. 回答中涉及结论性内容时，应尽量附带数据来源表单或字段说明。'
      ].join('\n');
    }

    function generateAgentDocs() {
      const name = document.getElementById('agentName').value || 'EnterpriseSupportAgent';
      const url = document.getElementById('projectUrl').value || 'http://localhost:8080';
      const dir = document.getElementById('workDir').value || '/workspace';
      const key = document.getElementById('apiKey').value || '{YOUR_API_KEY}';
      const role = document.getElementById('roleContent').value || '负责调用平台 OpenAPI、检索企业资料库并向业务侧提供准确答复。';
      const coreRules = selectedCoreRules();
      const companyName = basicConfig.company_name || '未配置企业名称';

      const docs = {
        AGENTS_MD: [
          `# Agent Node: ${name}`,
          `**Workspace**: \`${dir}\``,
          '',
          '## Agent Mission',
          `${name} 服务于 ${companyName}，用于检索企业基础信息和业务表单数据，并为后续客服或自动化流程提供统一上下文。`,
          '',
          '## Runtime Configuration',
          `- PROJECT_HOST: ${url}`,
          `- X-API-Key: ${key}`,
          '',
          enterpriseBlock(),
          '## Objectives',
          '1. 优先基于平台 API 与企业资料库回答问题。',
          '2. 保持返回内容与企业基础资料和业务表单一致。',
          '3. 在缺失字段时明确指出信息来源不足。',
          '',
          constraintBlock(),
          '',
          '## Core Rules',
          coreRules,
          '',
          apiUsageBlock(url, key)
        ].join('\n'),
        SOUL_MD: [
          '# Core Soul & Values',
          role,
          '',
          '## Working Principles',
          '1. 先核对企业资料，再引用业务数据。',
          '2. 对外描述必须与企业基本资料一致。',
          '3. 不编造企业地址、联系方式、官网或资质信息。',
          '',
          '## Core Rules',
          coreRules
        ].join('\n'),
        TOOLS_MD: [
          '# Configured Tools',
          `Base Context API Endpoint: \`${url}\``,
          `Authentication Header: \`X-API-Key: ${key}\``,
          '',
          '## Tooling Strategy',
          '- 第一步始终调用表单发现接口，确认授权范围与可用 schema。',
          '- 第二步读取目标表单字段定义，核对字段名、备注和含义。',
          '- 第三步按最小必要原则构造查询条件，并限制分页大小。',
          '- 第四步整理返回结果时注明来源表单与关键字段。',
          '',
          '## Recommended Calls',
          `- \`GET ${url}/openapi/forms\`：发现当前可访问表单`,
          `- \`GET ${url}/openapi/forms/{schema}\`：读取字段定义`,
          `- \`GET ${url}/openapi/forms/{schema}/data\`：查询实际数据`,
          '',
          '## Attached Business Context',
          `- 企业主体：${companyName}`,
          `- 企业官网：${basicConfig.company_website || '未设置'}`,
          '',
          apiUsageBlock(url, key),
          '',
          constraintBlock()
        ].join('\n'),
        IDENTITY_MD: [
          '# Persona & Identity',
          `Name: ${name}`,
          `Workspace: ${dir}`,
          `Primary Directive: 为 ${companyName} 提供可追溯、可调用的业务知识支撑。`,
          '',
          enterpriseBlock(),
          '## Core Rules',
          coreRules
        ].join('\n'),
        HEARTBEAT_MD: [
          '# Heartbeat Configuration',
          'Cron / Pulse Frequency: 5m',
          '',
          '## Health Check',
          `curl -I -H "X-API-Key: ${key}" ${url}/openapi/forms`,
          '',
          '## Background Context Refresh',
          `- 企业主体：${companyName}`,
          `- 企业官网：${basicConfig.company_website || '未设置'}`,
          '',
          '## Runtime Guardrails',
          '- 周期性自检仅验证接口可达性与授权有效性，不主动执行写入操作。',
          '- 若发现接口异常、鉴权失败或返回结构变化，应标记风险，不自行修复数据。',
          '- 心跳任务不得绕过表单发现步骤直接构造业务查询。'
        ].join('\n'),
        BOOTSTRAP_MD: [
          '# Bootstrapping Protocol',
          `1. 切换工作目录：\`cd ${dir}\``,
          '2. 校验 X-API-Key 已正确配置。',
          `3. 请求 \`${url}/openapi/forms\` 确认可访问表单。`,
          `4. 载入企业背景：${companyName}。`,
          `5. 加载核心规则并进入 READY 状态。`,
          '',
          '## Bootstrap Checks',
          '- 若 `/openapi/forms` 返回空列表，进入只读待命状态，不伪造业务能力。',
          '- 若企业基础信息缺失，保留能力但在输出中提示基础资料不完整。',
          '- 若 API Key 缺失或无效，停止后续所有表单调用。',
          '',
          '## Core Rules',
          coreRules
        ].join('\n'),
        MEMORY_MD: [
          '# Operational Memory',
          '## Permanent Context',
          `- Upstream base URL: \`${url}\``,
          `- API Token: \`${key}\``,
          `- Workspace: \`${dir}\``,
          '',
          enterpriseBlock(),
          '## Platform Guide',
          '- 调用平台所有接口时必须携带 `X-API-Key`。',
          '- 先通过 `/openapi/forms` 发现表单，再按 schema 获取字段和数据。',
          '- 企业基础信息以“基本设置”为准，业务明细以对应表单为准。',
          '',
          apiUsageBlock(url, key),
          '',
          constraintBlock(),
          '',
          '## Core Rules',
          coreRules,
          '',
          '## Short-term Notes',
          '_在运行时记录已发现的 schema code、关键字段和调用结果。_'
        ].join('\n')
      };

      Object.keys(docs).forEach((keyName) => {
        document.getElementById(`${keyName}_RAW`).innerText = docs[keyName];
      });

      showToast('Markdown 预览已生成');
    }
  </script>
